Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:05.62,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}逃げないで 逃れないで      
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.36,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}とどまって 立ち止まって    
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:13.46,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}そんな風に 適当言わないで  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:16.89,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}向き合って 向かい合って    
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:19.79,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}話し合って 愛し合って      
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:24.73,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}そんな風に たわごともうやめて 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:31.25,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}苦しかったら 我慢しないで  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.20,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}逃げちゃえ 壊れちゃう       
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.51,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}その前に                   
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:39.77,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}歌え踊れ 逃げろトレイシー  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:42.67,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}訳ありまくりのアイドル　   
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:47.81,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}リアルではさようなら       
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:51.22,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ここに戻って来るまで       
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.82,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}待ってていてね             
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.87,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}涙かくして えくそだすっ    
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.40,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}yeah yeah yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:43.43,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就算整個世界都怕得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.23,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}也不能垂頭喪氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:51.78,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}這是在浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.78,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}yeah yeah yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:56.69,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}yeah yeah yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.52,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}yeah yeah yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:05.62,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不要逃 不要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.36,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}停下腳步 老實站好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:13.46,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}這種話 請不要隨便說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:16.89,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}勇敢面對 坦誠相向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:19.79,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}互相溝通 互相友愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:24.73,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}這種玩笑 也請不要開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:31.25,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果覺得痛苦 請不要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.20,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}趕緊逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.51,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在壞掉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:39.77,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}唱吧跳吧 快逃吧 Tracy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:42.67,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}情非得已的idol
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:47.81,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在現實中永別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:51.22,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在我回到這裡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.82,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}要一直等著我哦
